    Instruction<op_t> *inst = new Instruction<op_t>();
    inst->type = src->type;
    inst->op = src->op;
    inst->reg = src->reg;
    inst->imm = src->imm;
    inst->src = src->src;
    inst->dest = src->dest;
    return inst;
}
